.DT
broadcast_to_channel
Disk World creator help
broadcast_to_channel

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
broadcast_to_channel -  Inform channel of message.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void broadcast_to_channel(mixed ob,
string channel,
mixed message)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object creating the channel event
%^BOLD%^channel%^RESET%^ - the channel to inform people about
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - the message to tell the channel about

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/broadcaster.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Inform channel of message.  The message will get sent to all the objects
added to the list to the method event_channel_message.  The method
will be called with three arguements, first is the object that started
the event, the second the channel it is being send to and the last is the
message being sent to the channel.
.EP

